snippet.title: [Stories to Tell] - Greyville Stay (Official Teaser Trailer)
snippet.description:
THE GAME WILL BE 100% FREE TO PLAY
Wishlist here (i think it helps) : https://store.steampowered.com/app/3240540/Stories_to_Tell_Greyville_Stay/
Discord : https://discord.gg/aEUxZscKUU

"Stories to Tell" Is a psychological horror game series developed by a 14 year old kid were each installment is based on a dream/nightmare me the developer has had. This is a game you wouldn't want to miss...

Music : @rickyedit - Gourmet
